{"sn2.28:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.28 ","sn2.28:0.2":"3. Nanatitthiyavagga ","sn2.28:0.3":"Nandivisalasutta ","sn2.28:1.1":"Ekamantam thito kho nandivisalo devaputto bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn2.28:2.1":"“Catucakkam navadvaram, ","sn2.28:2.2":"punnam lobhena samyutam; ","sn2.28:2.3":"Pankajatam mahavira, ","sn2.28:2.4":"katham yatra bhavissati”ti. ","sn2.28:3.1":"“Chetva naddhim varattanca, ","sn2.28:3.2":"icchalobhanca papakam; ","sn2.28:3.3":"Samulam tanhamabbuyha, ","sn2.28:3.4":"evam yatra bhavissati”ti. "}